<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interactive Aptitude Test</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #2d3748;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .question-container {
            display: none;
        }

        .question-container.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .question-container h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .option {
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .option:hover {
            background-color: #edf2f7;
        }

        .option input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 1rem;
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }

        .correct {
            background-color: #c6f6d5 !important;
            border-color: #48bb78 !important;
        }

        .incorrect {
            background-color: #fed7d7 !important;
            border-color: #f56565 !important;
        }

        .explanation {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            border-left: 4px solid #2b6cb0;
            padding: 1rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #2d3748;
            display: none;
        }

        .navigation-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        button {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, green 0%, lawngreen 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        button:disabled {
            background: #cbd5e0;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }

        #result {
            display: none;
            background: white;
            color: #2d3748;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .confetti {
            position: absolute;
            top: -50px;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background-color: blueviolet;
            opacity: 0.8;
            animation: fall 1s infinite ease-in-out;
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        @keyframes fall {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(0) translateY(-50px) rotate(0deg);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateX(calc(100vw - 10px)) translateY(calc(100vh - 50px)) rotate(360deg);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Aptitude Test</h1>
        <p>Answer the following questions:</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <form id="quizForm">
            <div id="quiz">
                <!-- Question 1 -->
                <div class="question-container active">
                    <h3>1. Is x greater than 0?</h3>
                    <div class="options">
                        <label class="option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="A">
                            A) Statement 1 alone is sufficient, but Statement 2 alone is not sufficient.
                        </label>
                        <label class="option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="B">
                            B) Statement 2 alone is sufficient, but Statement 1 alone is not sufficient.
                        </label>
                        <label class="option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="C">
                            C) Both statements together are sufficient, but neither statement alone is sufficient.
                        </label>
                        <label class="option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="D">
                            D) Each statement alone is sufficient.
                        </label>
                        <label class="option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="E">
                            E) Statements 1 and 2 together are not sufficient.
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="explanation" id="explanation-q11">
                        <p>The correct answer is C) Both statements together are sufficient, but neither statement alone is sufficient. 
                        Statement 1: x² > 0, which is true for any x except 0 but doesn't specify whether x is positive or negative. 
                        Statement 2: x is not negative. Together, these indicate x > 0.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="question-container">
                    <h3>2. What is the value of y?</h3>
