                        Statement 1 and Statement 2 together confirm the properties of the triangle to classify it as isosceles.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question-container">
                    <h3>8. Is p a prime number?</h3>
                    <div class="options">
                        <label class="option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="A">
                            A) Statement 1 alone is sufficient, but Statement 2 alone is not sufficient.
                        </label>
                        <label class="option">
                            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="B">
